div.p:
"Not every one that saith unto me, Lord, Lord, shall enter into the kingdom of heaven; but he
that doeth the will of my Father which is in heaven" (Matt. 7:21);
"And all saints who
remember to keep and do these sayings" (D&C 89:18);
". . . but the doers of the law shall be
justified" (Rom. 2:13);
"Whosoever cometh to me, and heareth my sayings, and doeth them"
(Luke 6:47)—these are the admonitions.
